description: For draft warehouse shops, obtain all parameters with privilege that have not been SWAPPED to pickup product, whether_id and address_id. Corresponding to 2 order/get_warehouse_deliver_config states (more logic about warehouse draft has been optimized that do not need product_number_id and time) (time has been SWAPPED), gets data that have same status like default warehouse with default product_whether_id and EDITED time

parameters.name: partner_id
parameters.description: Partner ID is assigned when registration is successful. Required for all requests.

parameters.name: timestamp
parameters.description: This is to indicate the timestamp of the request. Required for all requests. Expires in 5 minutes.

parameters.name: access_token
parameters.description: The token for API access, using to identify your permission to the api. Used for multi-use and expires in 4 hours.

parameters.name: shop_id
parameters.description: Shopper's unique identifier for a shop. Required param for shop APIs.

children.name: warehouse_name
children.description: The warehouse name field in when creating the warehouse address

children.name: warehouse_type
children.description:
Type of warehouse. Applicable values:
1. Local Warehouse
2. OS Warehouse

children.name: product_location_id
children.description: Location identifier for pickup. Different location_ids represent that your addresses are at different time status.
